      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This car is in good condition. It runs and drives well, with no major mechanical issues. The exterior has minor wear \u2014 a few small scratches and light scuffs \u2014 but no significant dents or damage. The paint is in decent shape and holds up well overall. The interior is clean and functional, showing normal use but no tears or major staining. A solid, reliable vehicle.",
      "price": 33500.0,
